00:36:09.586 --> 00:36:11.170
And then it's just.
at some point.

760
00:36:11.171 --> 00:36:16.175
this. like. the strangest
thing happened where I... uh.

761
00:36:16.176 --> 00:36:18.470
actually. I did.

